===========================
The first major release! Here's the changes:

    * Lots of changes
    * Bugfixes (one took me a month to fix!)
    * Examples


pysocket 0.9.0 (2015-04-18)
===========================
Here's the list of changes in v0.9.0:

    * More documentation
    * Made pysocket totally asynchronous


pysocket 0.8.0 (2015-04-17)
===========================
Version 0.8 includes (sparse) documentation and small changes. Here's the list:

    * Completed some of the documentation
    * Some changes to the code
    * Addtions to the code


pysocket 0.7.0 (2015-03-31)
===========================
Pre-release for version 0.8. Mostly documentation work. Here's what's new:

    * Started on the documentation
    * Rewrote the README
    * Some additions to the server class


pysocket 0.6.0 (2015-03-30)
===========================
This release includes:

    * Server base class
    * Client base class
    * Small improvments


pysocket 0.5.0 (2015-03-27)
===========================
Major release, because of py3k compatiblity and improvments generally. Here's the changes:

    * Full py3k support
    * A few improvments
    * Bugfixes


pysocket 0.4.0 (2015-03-27)
===========================
Pre-release for version 0.5. Here's whats new for now:

    * Some py3k support
    * Improvments
